{"tid":2159894,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"黃世澤：只要無DQ，其實做多一年議員有咩所謂？","createTime":"2020-08-16T15:12:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T15:14:42.000Z","uid":219007,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"253d4ba7d1f8b77edc1d2d79b3761bfa6201d5af","tid":2159894,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T15:12:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5AgU6OhMuc8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5AgU6OhMuc8&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJGCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=a67afac0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5AgU6OhMuc8</a><br />\n<br />\n黃世澤（下亞厘畢道）：<br />\n<br />\n總辭與否首先要從戰略考慮出發，唔需要理會黃毓民同熱狗，因為佢哋係幫中共做嘢，所以佢地係唔會從戰略考慮到諗野。<br />\n<br />\n只要延任一年下無DQ冇乜，其實做多一年有乜所謂？ 泛民繼續好似以往咁樣癱瘓議會就得啦。 今次延任一年同當年臨立會唔同，嗰陣係九七之前架空左立法會，所以我絕對唔會原諒馮檢基。"},{"pid":"c95de22617f7792b2ed73db2bf1b54c68bad5e04","tid":2159894,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T15:13:19.000Z","msg":"noted with thanks"},{"pid":"0a1126a69a07d6845b685aa8fc1cb1e29430c226","tid":2159894,"uid":118217,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T15:13:38.000Z","msg":"反正啲內會投票都輸<br />\n表態反對中央都係好事"},{"pid":"6842119505f5a4f948c00697caf9c035aee8604f","tid":2159894,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T15:14:42.000Z","msg":"世柒: 我要泛民喺議會入面篤眼篤鼻，why make their life so easy ?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2159878\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2159878</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}